          You have ₹6 lakh sitting in your bank account. Should you invest it all at once
          (lumpsum) or split it into ₹5,000 monthly SIPs over 10 years? The internet says
          different things. Here's the honest answer — with real calculations, real scenarios,
          and one counter-intuitive truth most advisors won't tell you.
        </p>
